header: Test vectors of type RsaOeapDecrypt check decryption with OAEP.

Constructed.description: The test vector (i.e. seed and label) has been constructed so that the padded plaintext em has some special properties.

EncryptionWithLabel.description: RSA-OAEP allows an optional parameter label, that is associated with the message. This test vector contains a ciphertext that was encrypted with a non-empty label.

Normal.description: The test vector contains a pseudorandomly generated, valid test case. Implementations are expected to pass this test.

SmallModulus.description: The key for this test vector has a modulus of size < 2048.
